    <div class="container">
        <h2>Easy Banana Pancakes</h2>
        <p>Make delicious and fluffy banana pancakes with simple ingredients.</p>
        <h3>Ingredients</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>1 ripe banana</li>
            <li>1 cup flour</li>
            <li>1 teaspoon baking powder</li>
            <li>1 tablespoon sugar</li>
            <li>1 egg</li>
            <li>1/2 cup milk</li>
            <li>1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract</li>
            <li>1 tablespoon melted butter</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Instructions</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Mash the banana in a bowl.</li>
            <li>Add egg, milk, vanilla, and melted butter. Mix well.</li>
            <li>In another bowl, mix flour, baking powder, and sugar.</li>
            <li>Combine wet and dry ingredients until smooth.</li>
            <li>Heat a pan and pour batter to make pancakes.</li>
            <li>Cook until golden brown, then flip.</li>
            <li>Serve and enjoy!</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
